\int_\mathbb{R} K_{\sigma}(x-y)dx=\int_\mathbb{R} e^{-(x-y)^2/2\sigma^2}dx=\sigma\int_\mathbb{R} e^{-t^2/2}dt=\sigma\sqrt{2\pi}
